y-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">Asia was named the <a href="/2024/4/23/24138101/asia-climate-change-weather-disasters-wmo-report">most disaster-prone region</a> in the world. Sweltering temperatures forced government officials in the Philippines <a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-dangerous-heat-prompts-shift-online-classes-power-crunch-2024-04-29/">to close schools</a>. </p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/04/30/climate/settlement-resurfaces-philippines-climate-dam-scli-intl/index.html" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">A 300-year-old settlement resurfaces as severe drought dries up a dam in the Philippines | CNN</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->CNN<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card group relative z-10 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-cc bg-white py-16 text-black last-of-type:border-b-0 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:border-gray-31 dark:bg-gray-13 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-md sm:pl-20 sm:pr-60 lg:py-40"><div class="flex items-center"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd relative z-10 mr-20 hidden md:block -rotate-180 border-l border-l-blurple pl-4 dark:border-l-franklin" style="writing-mode:vertical-lr;text-orientation:sideways"><a href="/climate-change">Climate</a></span>