hange-report">supply chain</a> by 2030. By the same date, Apple also plans to replenish fresh water it uses in drought-stressed areas — spending $8 million on that task since 2023.</p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="relative z-10 font-polysans leading-120"><a class="text-16 leading-120 text-gray-4a shadow-underline-blurple hover:text-blurple dark:text-gray-ef dark:shadow-underline-franklin dark:hover:text-franklin" href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/04/apple-ramps-up-investment-in-clean-energy-and-water-around-the-world/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Apple ramps up investment in clean energy and water around the world</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->Apple Newsroom<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card group relative z-10 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-cc bg-white py-16 text-black last-of-type:border-b-0 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:border-gray-31 dark:bg-gray-13 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-md sm:pl-20 sm:pr-60 lg:py-40"><div class="flex items-center"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd relative z-10 mr-20 hidden md:block -rotate-180 border-l border-l-blurple pl-4 dark:border-l-franklin" style="writing-mode:vertical-lr;text-orientation:sideways"><a href="/climate-change">Climate</a></span><div class="max-w-content-block-mobile sm:w-content-block-standard sm:max-w-content-block-standard"><div class="mb-6 flex md:hidden"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd border-b border-b-blurple pb-4 dark:border-b-franklin" style="writing-mode:initial;text-orientation:initial"><a href="/climate-change">Climate</a></span></div><h2 class="font-polysans 