ext-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">These companies are trying to alter the atmosphere as the world makes slow progress to tackle climate change, <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/03/31/climate/climate-change-carbon-capture-ccs.html?utm_source=cbnewsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_term=2024-04-02&utm_campaign=Daily+Briefing+02+04+2024"><em>The New York Times</em></a> reports. </p><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin">If you want to learn more about how these technologies work and what could go wrong, <em>The Verge</em> has explainers on <a href="/2021/9/9/22663597/largest-direct-air-capture-plant-c02-climeworks-iceland">machines</a> that <a href="/2023/9/7/23863386/microsoft-heirloom-biden-administrations-carbon-removal-hub">suck</a> <a href="/2023/9/12/23869817/amazon-climate-carbon-removal-purchase-occidental-petroleum">CO2</a> <a href="/2023/8/14/23831268/carbon-removal-climate-change-biden-funding-energy-department">out of the air</a> <a href="/2023/5/4/23711098/ocean-carbon-removal-california-captura-climate-change">and</a> <a href="/2023/5/4/23711098/ocean-carbon-removal-california-captura-climate-change">ocean</a> and <a href="/2023/2/24/23613293/solar-geoengineering-mexico-us-reno-nevada-faa-make-sunsets">attempts</a> to <a href="/2024/3/21/24107762/marine-cloud-brightening-climate-change-science-advances">reflect</a> <a href="/24087552/solar-geoengineering-international-rules-stalemate">sunlight</a> back into space. </p><br/></div><div class="pt-12"><div class="duet--media--embed min-h-[100px] quickpost mb-0 w-full relative z-10 overflow-x-hidden md:max-w-full"></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card group relative z-10 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-cc bg-white py-16 text-black last-of-type:border-b-0 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:border-gray-31 dark:bg-gray-13 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-md sm:pl-20 sm:pr-60 lg:py-40"><div class="flex items-center"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd relative z-10 mr-20 hidden md:block -rotate-180 border-l border-l-blurple pl-4 dark:border-l-franklin" style="writing-mode:vertical-lr;text-orientation:sideways"><a href="/climate-change">Climate</a></span><div class="max-w-content-block-mobile sm:w-content-block-standard sm:max-w-content-block-standard"><div class="mb-6 flex md:hidden"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd border-b border-b-blurple pb-4 dark:border-b-franklin" style="writing-mode:initial;text-orientation:initial"><a href="/climate-change">Climate</a></span></div><h2 class="font-polysans text-20 font-bold leading-100 tracking-1 md:text-24"><a class="after:absolute after:inset-0 group-hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:group-hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/2024/3/29/24114896/heavy-duty-vehicles-trucks-pollution-standards-climate-change-biden-epa">The US tightens greenhouse gas emission standards for heavy-duty vehicles</a></h2><div class="relative z-10 inline-block pt-4 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-140 tracking-15 text-gray-31 dark:text-gray-bd"><div class="inline-block"><a class="text-gray-31 hover:shadow-underline-inherit dark:text-franklin mr-8" href="/authors/justine-calma">Justi